Revision history for Perl module Test::DataDriven.

0.03  Sat Nov 25 15:40:30 CET 2006
    - Allow declaring per-handler filters using attributes.
    - Include some missing files in the distribution.

0.02  Sun Feb 12 15:44:11 UTC 2006
    - Fixed registering plugins by regular expression.
    - Added stop_run method to stop tests.
    - Default to 'Test::DataDriven' in Test::DataDriven::Plugin::register.
    - Allow Test::DataDriven to be require()d by
      ExtUtils::MakeMaker/Module::Build when checking prerequisites.

0.01  Thu Feb 09 21:38:44 CET 2006
    - First public release.
